stripe down the side of it.

10:19.486 --> 10:20.654
It was awesome.

10:20.721 --> 10:24.457
- Well I'll have to look
it up then, Starsky.

10:24.457 --> 10:27.795
- No, Starsky.

10:27.795 --> 10:29.162
- Yeah?

10:29.196 --> 10:30.463
- You fell for the
oldest trick in the book,

10:30.463 --> 10:31.932
