12:16.036 --> 12:18.638
(dog barking)

12:23.543 --> 12:25.545
- Definitely not like London.

12:25.578 --> 12:26.579
Phone booths work.

12:34.387 --> 12:35.622
(bells tolling)

12:35.622 --> 12:39.259
- There she is, in all
her glory, the church.

12:40.593 --> 12:43.130
