13:00.747 --> 13:02.682
I thought that on this
job you have to be,

13:02.715 --> 13:04.717
you have to be
vigilant all the time.

13:04.717 --> 13:06.119
- Vigilant?

13:06.153 --> 13:08.155
You'll soon find out
nothing happens 'round here.

13:08.221 --> 13:10.723
- Well, my training
taught me to be prepared

13:10.757 --> 13:13.126
for anything and
everything at any time,

13:13.126 --> 13:14.928
day or night, on duty or off.

13:16.429 --> 13:18.465
- Well, I tell you something
they aint prepared you for.

13:18.465 --> 13:19.366
- What's that?

13:19.432 --> 13:21.234
- Boredom, sheer boredom.

13:21.301 --> 13:22.502
Nothing happens 'round here.

13:22.502 --> 13:24.838
It's like a morgue
in a recession.

13:24.838 --> 13:26.673
- Well, then maybe
we need to go out

13:26.673 --> 13:27.574
and find crime, you know,

13:27.640 --> 13:29.042
I mean it happens it everywhere.

13:29.042 --> 13:31.044
They say it's just hidden
behind closed doors.

13:31.078 --> 13:34.882
- I used to be just like you
when I first started, keen.

13:34.882 --> 13:36.216
- And how long ago was that?

13:36.249 --> 13:38.285
