14:01.909 --> 14:02.910
No.

14:02.943 --> 14:05.212
That's why you're P.C. Brody,

14:05.212 --> 14:07.347
stop being so PC, Bruce.

14:08.548 --> 14:10.117
- Well government
guidelines suggest

14:10.183 --> 14:11.418
that we should
actually investigate

14:11.418 --> 14:13.453
all hate crime initiators, so.

14:14.554 --> 14:15.923
- It's like living in the past.

14:15.923 --> 14:18.325
