day after day after day.

14:24.497 --> 14:25.832
- There's must be some crime.

14:25.865 --> 14:28.201
Otherwise that would
mean Little Pitchfield

14:28.235 --> 14:30.170
is literally a
crime free location.

14:30.170 --> 14:31.638
- Let me tell you something.

14:31.671 --> 14:34.241
Little Pitchfield has been
off every crime report

14:34.241 --> 14:37.177
and statistic in
the last 17 years.

14:37.210 --> 14:39.012
