16:33.793 --> 16:35.462
Well do you get me?

16:35.462 --> 16:36.329
- Yes, sir.

16:36.363 --> 16:38.665
- Well do ya, punk?

16:38.665 --> 16:40.467
- Yes, sir.

16:40.467 --> 16:41.468
- (laughs) Did you get it?

16:41.468 --> 16:43.803
