17:45.165 --> 17:47.700
Anyway, we could see
it in Great Pitchfield

17:47.767 --> 17:49.302
about three miles away.

17:49.336 --> 17:50.470
I mean, it was a
really clear night

17:50.470 --> 17:52.172
and I remember
because there was me,

17:52.172 --> 17:55.742
Billy, Drake, Bob,
Sandra, Ellen,

17:56.709 --> 17:58.445
