Listen, Sandra and Bob were
looking out into the distance

18:32.179 --> 18:34.847
and to the left of the
fireworks, Bob could see

18:34.881 --> 18:36.849
this bright white light.

18:38.218 --> 18:39.786
Well he did point it out
to me, come to think of it,

18:39.819 --> 18:41.288
but I just dismissed it.

18:41.288 --> 18:42.955
I thought it was just,
you know, other fireworks.

18:42.989 --> 18:44.591
But anyway, listen,
all of a sudden

18:44.591 --> 18:46.058
there was a power surge.

18:46.092 --> 18:48.161
The whole village went
out and back on again.

18:48.161 --> 18:50.197
Well, Sally and
Bernard stopped humping

18:50.263 --> 18:51.464
and started howling.

18:51.464 --> 18:52.765
That made me look
across the field

18:52.799 --> 18:55.302
and there was this
bright white light.

18:55.302 --> 18:58.037
We could all see it, this one,

18:58.070 --> 19:02.242
and all of a sudden it
just and it was gone

19:02.242 --> 19:05.412
but in a completely different
direction to the fireworks.

19:07.714 --> 19:09.949
- You know, I mean, those lights

19:10.016 --> 19:12.084
could have been anything, right?

19:12.084 --> 19:13.386
- Yeah, maybe.

19:13.420 --> 19:14.887
