- [Radio] Calling PS Cooper,
PS Cooper, are you there?

26:15.541 --> 26:16.709
- Yeah, receiving, over.

26:16.743 --> 26:17.677
- [Radio] Breaking
and entering reported

26:17.710 --> 26:19.211
