26:19.211 --> 26:21.714
Suspects on site,
I see one male,

26:21.714 --> 26:22.715
and I see one female.

26:22.749 --> 26:25.284
Also reports of IC9 in location.

26:25.317 --> 26:27.253
- Yeah, on route.

26:27.253 --> 26:28.254
What's on IC9?

26:28.254 --> 26:29.255
- IC9 is unknown.

26:29.288 --> 26:30.489
- Oh right.

26:30.556 --> 26:31.457
- Where's Little
Pitchfield Manor?

26:31.457 --> 26:32.158
- Just 'round the corner.

26:32.224 --> 26:32.959
- There?
- Yeah.

26:32.959 --> 26:33.793
- Come on.

26:35.294 --> 26:40.299
(alarm ringing)
(tense music)

26:44.336 --> 26:46.372
- Oi, what are you doing?

26:47.640 --> 26:49.575
- I'm going in.

26:49.575 --> 26:51.010
- No, hang on.

26:51.043 --> 26:54.213
I've got to get my
breath back, first.

26:56.916 --> 26:59.085
- Are we going in or not?

26:59.118 --> 27:00.486
- Hang on.

27:00.552 --> 27:04.056
Jesus, you scared
the shit out of me.

27:04.090 --> 27:05.324
- I just got here.

27:05.324 --> 27:06.826
Got scared, didn't
want to go inside

27:06.859 --> 27:08.761
