(eerie tense music)

32:24.343 --> 32:27.213
(ethereal roaring)

32:39.425 --> 32:41.660
(coughing)

32:45.131 --> 32:48.034
(ethereal roaring)

32:49.301 --> 32:52.304
(eerie tense music)

33:20.132 --> 33:23.035
(ethereal roaring)

33:42.954 --> 33:44.823
(shouts)

33:44.890 --> 33:46.092
Did you lose it?

33:46.092 --> 33:46.992
- There are no weapons.

33:47.059 --> 33:49.528
- What do they look like then?

33:52.631 --> 33:53.532
- Run, run.

33:55.334 --> 33:58.337
(eerie tense music)

34:01.640 --> 34:02.741
- Brody, wait!

34:04.710 --> 34:05.544
Wait.

34:13.919 --> 34:15.154
- Come on!

34:15.154 --> 34:16.322
- Wait for me.

34:19.558 --> 34:22.461
(ethereal roaring)

34:29.835 --> 34:32.838
(eerie tense music)

34:56.962 --> 34:58.330
Shit, go, go, go.

35:28.794 --> 35:30.996
(shouting)

35:31.029 --> 35:32.030
Quick, help us.

35:32.030 --> 35:32.864
We've got people here.

35:32.864 --> 35:33.699
- What?

35:37.369 --> 35:38.537
- Get it up.

35:38.570 --> 35:40.071
What happened here?

35:40.071 --> 35:41.907
No, put your end down.

35:44.376 --> 35:47.213
(groaning)

35:47.246 --> 35:50.249
(eerie tense music)

35:55.086 --> 35:56.422
(groaning)

35:56.422 --> 35:57.923
- [Brody] Push it.

36:00.759 --> 36:01.660
Some chairs, some chairs.

36:01.660 --> 36:03.529
- Okay, I'll block it up.

36:16.675 --> 36:21.680
(ethereal growling)
(gunshot)

36:24.383 --> 36:27.118
- Man, you said,
you said nothing

36:27.118 --> 36:29.555
ever happens here, normally.

36:30.922 --> 36:31.823
- It don't.

36:33.259 --> 36:34.760
That's not normal.

36:37.996 --> 36:41.333
Apart from that runaway
a couple of days ago.

36:44.169 --> 36:45.871
- What runaway?

36:45.871 --> 36:49.375
(ethereal growling)
(screaming)

36:49.408 --> 36:52.411
(eerie tense music)

37:17.669 --> 37:19.538
Hello, is anyone there?

37:19.571 --> 37:20.406
This is PC Brody.

37:22.574 --> 37:27.279
We need immediate backup
