37:54.005 --> 37:55.807
- What do you think it is?

37:56.675 --> 37:57.509
- Zombies?

37:58.544 --> 37:59.545
- I knew it.

38:00.912 --> 38:04.516
- Our barricade's not
gonna hold them for long.

38:05.451 --> 38:06.284
- Jesus.

38:09.455 --> 38:11.390
Joe, do you hear me?

38:14.125 --> 38:15.160
It's Shaun Cooper.

38:16.462 --> 38:17.363
We're at the old manor house.

38:17.363 --> 38:18.930
Look, we need backup now.

38:18.964 --> 38:22.334
There's just dozens of
them, like creatures.

38:22.334 --> 38:23.168
- IC9s.

38:24.135 --> 38:26.304
- IC9s, do you hear me, over.

38:27.673 --> 38:31.009
- Well, what do we do now?

38:31.009 --> 38:34.179
- We hold them off and
we wait for backup.

38:34.212 --> 38:35.246
Yeah?

38:35.246 --> 38:36.582
- Look, I agree.

38:38.216 --> 38:41.219
(eerie tense music)

38:57.503 --> 38:59.505
(farts)

39:02.040 --> 39:03.341
- Better out than in.

39:03.341 --> 39:04.776
- Oh please.

39:04.843 --> 39:08.847
- I'm sorry, I just get
