39:08.880 --> 39:09.781
- [Ellen] We're all nervous.

39:09.781 --> 39:11.417
Just try to control yourself.

39:11.417 --> 39:13.885
- Hey, it looks
like they're gone.

39:13.919 --> 39:15.153
- No, no I don't care.

39:15.153 --> 39:16.655
