to sit and do nothing?

39:20.091 --> 39:22.093
- Well it sounds like
a great plan to me.

39:22.127 --> 39:24.162
- It's been two
hours and nothing.

39:24.195 --> 39:26.031
- Calm down.

39:26.031 --> 39:28.166
