- Well look, we
can't risk it okay.

39:51.156 --> 39:52.658
- I was my college record holder

39:52.658 --> 39:53.725
over 100 metre sprint.

39:53.759 --> 39:55.927
I will be in and out.

39:55.961 --> 39:57.295
I know where it is.

39:57.295 --> 39:58.430
- Don't go.

39:58.464 --> 39:59.465
Stay here.

39:59.465 --> 40:00.799
- Dan, Dan, Dan.

40:01.967 --> 40:03.201
Come back through
the barricade, okay.

40:03.201 --> 40:04.002
It's not safe out there.
- I will be two minutes.

40:04.002 --> 40:05.003
I'll be right back.

40:05.871 --> 40:07.539
- Fuck's sake.

40:07.539 --> 40:10.942
(tense electronic music)

40:18.083 --> 40:21.086
(ethereal growling)

40:22.954 --> 40:25.457
(tense electronic music)

40:25.457 --> 40:28.359
(ethereal roaring)

40:34.800 --> 40:37.202
(screeching)

40:52.383 --> 40:55.253
(ethereal roaring)

41:04.129 --> 41:07.533
(tense electronic music)

41:16.675 --> 41:18.877
(shouting)

41:21.212 --> 41:23.549
(screaming)

41:27.452 --> 41:32.457
(ethereal roaring)
(wet guttural screaming)

41:48.840 --> 41:51.610
(low tense music)

42:09.861 --> 42:13.331
- Well, at least the
power's still on.

42:14.700 --> 42:17.202
- Think they're still out there?

42:17.235 --> 42:19.738
- Of course they're
still out there.

42:19.805 --> 42:21.139
You should have stopped him.

42:21.172 --> 42:22.340
You should have made him stay.

42:22.340 --> 42:24.009
- It's not within our
remit to use force

42:24.009 --> 42:25.510
or aggression to
control a situation.

42:25.543 --> 42:27.212
Okay, we deescalate.

42:27.212 --> 42:28.546
- Deescalate.
- Yeah.

42:28.580 --> 42:30.749
- PC Brody was
only doing his job.

42:30.782 --> 42:32.217
- You shut up.

42:32.217 --> 42:33.985
You wanted to press
charges and now he's dead.

42:34.052 --> 42:35.921
- Why don't you all shut up?

42:35.921 --> 42:38.256
- It's the end of the world!

42:39.457 --> 42:40.558
I've seen it.

42:41.760 --> 42:45.597
I've seen it for
nigh on 30 years.

42:45.597 --> 42:49.400
In my dreams and
nightmares, this is it.

42:52.570 --> 42:54.072
- What are you talking about?

42:54.072 --> 42:58.944
- I'm telling you straight,
I've seen it before, in visions.

43:02.614 --> 43:05.416
Nigh, it is out there.

43:06.384 --> 43:08.720
Nigh, it is waiting.

43:10.288 --> 43:11.122
- [Ellen] Who?

43:12.891 --> 43:13.725
- Them.

43:15.126 --> 43:16.928
- So not zombies then?

43:16.962 --> 43:20.766
- Zombies is like a
picnic compared to this.

43:23.669 --> 43:26.304
17 years ago, do you remember?

43:26.304 --> 43:31.242
17 years ago they came
a-looking, stalking

43:32.878 --> 43:35.346
like burglars looking
'round a house

43:35.346 --> 43:36.915
they're gonna raid.

43:37.849 --> 43:39.284
- He's right.

43:39.284 --> 43:42.287
- This aint no zombies.

43:44.756 --> 43:46.424
This aint gonna end.

43:48.794 --> 43:52.597
Nobody's coming to save us.

43:52.597 --> 43:54.866
We have to save ourselves.

43:56.902 --> 43:58.536
- He's right.

43:58.536 --> 44:00.205
It's aliens!

44:00.238 --> 44:01.406
- [Ellen] How can
you be so excited?

44:01.472 --> 44:03.975
- 'Cause for once in my life

44:04.009 --> 44:05.543
I get to be Sigourney Weaver.

44:06.945 --> 44:10.081
Look, I might just have a way
of getting us out of this.

44:10.081 --> 44:11.116
- [Brody] Okay, so
what's the plan then?

44:11.182 --> 44:13.618
- Weapons, bloody loads of them.

44:13.618 --> 44:15.821
Bob, where are those weapons?

44:15.887 --> 44:18.724
(low eerie music)

44:20.425 --> 44:21.760
Bob, Bob wait wait.

44:21.760 --> 44:22.794
- What?

44:22.828 --> 44:24.629
- Give me the weapon.

44:24.629 --> 44:25.931
- It's mine.

44:25.964 --> 44:27.132
- Now, I don't like
this as much as you do

44:27.132 --> 44:29.735
but give me the weapon.

44:29.801 --> 44:31.903
Now stay behind me.

44:31.903 --> 44:33.171
Not that close.

44:41.379 --> 44:43.014
Absolute silence.

44:43.048 --> 44:44.282
- That be good.

44:51.556 --> 44:54.525
(eerie tense music)

45:35.433 --> 45:37.903
(eerie music)

45:51.382 --> 45:53.484
- Where are those weapons, Bob?

45:53.484 --> 45:57.655
- In the greenhouse,
out by the allotment.

45:57.655 --> 45:58.489
- Come on.

45:59.390 --> 46:02.293
(eerie tense music)

46:06.798 --> 46:10.001
(electrical crackling)

46:35.927 --> 46:37.095
- There it be.

46:37.128 --> 46:38.129
- Wait, wait, wait.

46:38.129 --> 46:40.498
Is that one of the creatures?

46:42.000 --> 46:43.668
- He looks buggered.

46:43.668 --> 46:45.036
- No, they don't.

46:47.172 --> 46:49.007
- Are we gonna go or what?

46:49.007 --> 46:50.475
- Oh come on, Bob.

46:50.475 --> 46:51.843
We've all seen
enough of them films

46:51.843 --> 46:53.378
to know it's not dead.

46:53.411 --> 46:55.213
It's just laying there
waiting for us to approach

46:55.213 --> 46:57.015
and when we do it will be alive.

46:58.383 --> 47:01.552
- I'll bash it with this.

47:01.586 --> 47:02.587
- That won't work.

47:02.620 --> 47:04.890
It will still be alive.

47:04.923 --> 47:08.126
(eerie tense music)

47:08.126 --> 47:09.294
- Are you gonna
make a decision soon

47:09.327 --> 47:10.328
or others will come.

47:12.130 --> 47:14.966
- All right, come
on, let's do it.

47:24.175 --> 47:26.377
(growling)

47:30.715 --> 47:31.883
- There it be.

47:39.457 --> 47:40.625
- Thundercats!

47:41.692 --> 47:44.695
(eerie tense music)

47:56.407 --> 47:58.376
- That's Billy.

47:58.376 --> 47:59.577
- Can't be.

47:59.610 --> 48:00.912
We only seen him
a few hours ago.

48:00.912 --> 48:02.847
- That's definitely him.

48:02.880 --> 48:04.882
- That means whatever's
infected them

48:04.882 --> 48:07.218
is killing them in
just a couple of hours.

48:07.252 --> 48:09.087
(ethereal roaring)

48:09.120 --> 48:10.922
(gunshot)

48:10.922 --> 48:12.323
- Thank you.

48:12.390 --> 48:15.360
(eerie tense music)

48:18.663 --> 48:21.599
(ethereal roaring)

49:14.052 --> 49:15.720
- It's them.

49:15.720 --> 49:17.155
They're coming for us now.

49:17.155 --> 49:18.723
- It's okay, it's okay.

49:18.756 --> 49:19.657
It's gonna be fine.

49:19.657 --> 49:22.027
It's gonna be absolutely fine.

49:23.761 --> 49:25.430
Oi, Katie, what are you doing?

49:26.464 --> 49:27.832
- I can get out.

49:27.832 --> 49:29.534
They're distracted
with those two.

49:29.600 --> 49:30.501
I can get out.

49:30.501 --> 49:32.837
- No, no, just, uh, don't move.

49:32.837 --> 49:34.672
- You didn't stop Dan.

49:34.672 --> 49:35.740
Why would you stop me?

49:36.707 --> 49:39.610
- [Brody] Katie!

49:39.677 --> 49:44.015
Fuck's sake.

49:44.049 --> 49:47.052
(eerie tense music)

49:52.757 --> 49:57.762
(ethereal roaring)
(eerie tense music)

50:13.544 --> 50:15.880
(screaming)

50:17.182 --> 50:19.684
(tense music)

50:29.760 --> 50:30.761
- What's wrong?

50:30.761 --> 50:32.530
- It's my leg, it really hurts.

50:32.530 --> 50:34.265
- Is it where Billy grabbed ya?

50:34.299 --> 50:38.203
- No, no I scarped it on
an old tree stump just now.

50:38.203 --> 50:40.371
- Tell me the truth, Bob.

50:41.639 --> 50:43.541
- Nothing happened.

50:44.942 --> 50:46.444
- No it's not.

50:46.511 --> 50:47.612
It's where Billy, that
creature, grabbed you

50:47.612 --> 50:49.380
and now you're infected.

50:49.380 --> 50:50.615
You're gonna turn into
one of them monsters.

50:50.681 --> 50:53.551
- It was just an old
tree stump, I tell ya.

50:53.551 --> 50:54.385
- You're lying!

50:56.087 --> 50:57.388
- [Bob] You don't believe me?

50:57.388 --> 50:58.589
- If you turn into
one of them things

50:58.589 --> 50:59.990
I'll blow your
bleeding head off.

51:00.057 --> 51:02.427
- [Bob] I'm telling you
the truth, believe me.

51:02.460 --> 51:05.463
(eerie tense music)

51:06.297 --> 51:07.632
- Okay, come on.

51:11.336 --> 51:14.339
(eerie tense music)

51:42.333 --> 51:44.502
(ethereal roaring)

51:44.535 --> 51:46.671
(gunshot)

51:52.343 --> 51:53.344
Brody, Brody!

51:54.279 --> 51:55.079
Brody.

51:56.247 --> 51:57.081
Brody!

51:57.081 --> 51:58.349
- Oh, shit.

51:58.383 --> 52:00.951
- [Cooper] Here, take this.

52:00.951 --> 52:03.321
(tense music)

52:18.303 --> 52:20.505
- We thought you were dead.

52:28.446 --> 52:31.048
- Wait, where's Katie?

52:31.048 --> 52:33.384
- It's nothing.
- She's gone.

52:33.384 --> 52:34.385
I couldn't stop her.

52:37.822 --> 52:38.823
What's happened?

52:38.889 --> 52:40.658
- There's dozens of em.

52:40.658 --> 52:43.027
Look, I need to speak to you.

52:45.162 --> 52:47.765
One of them creatures was Billy.

52:47.798 --> 52:48.933
- Billy?

52:48.933 --> 52:50.201
Pissed up the tree Billy?

52:50.201 --> 52:51.035
- Yeah.

52:52.670 --> 52:55.072
That means this must be a virus

52:55.139 --> 52:58.142
and I'm guessing it's passed
on by physical contact.

52:58.175 --> 53:00.110
- Does that mean
it could actually

53:00.110 --> 53:01.779
be a chemical weapon's attack?

53:01.846 --> 53:03.848
- No, not in Little Pitchfield.

53:03.881 --> 53:05.750
Anyway, it's not airborne.

53:06.917 --> 53:09.454
- All right, what
weapons did we get?

53:09.487 --> 53:11.121
- Let's do our weapon's check.

53:15.260 --> 53:18.263
(eerie tense music)

53:44.322 --> 53:45.923
Have you had any
weapons training?

53:45.923 --> 53:47.057
- Oh yeah.

53:47.091 --> 53:48.593
We had a weeks intensive
combat training.

53:48.593 --> 53:52.797
Trust me, I know my
way a few of these.

53:52.797 --> 53:53.931
- How is he?

53:53.964 --> 53:55.466
- We need a doctor.

53:55.466 --> 53:57.001
- What now?

53:57.001 --> 53:59.670
Come here, I need to talk to ya.

54:01.071 --> 54:04.074
You know I said one of
them creatures was Billy?

54:04.141 --> 54:06.043
We see him less
than 24 hours ago.

54:08.546 --> 54:11.416
Yeah, well he was half
dead before I killed him.

54:11.416 --> 54:13.083
This could only mean one thing.

54:13.117 --> 54:14.619
- What?

54:14.619 --> 54:16.487
- This aint just a virus.

54:16.554 --> 54:18.155
It's an annihilation.

54:18.155 --> 54:19.390
We're being exterminated.

54:20.558 --> 54:23.528
(ethereal growling)

54:24.462 --> 54:25.296
You promised me!

54:27.298 --> 54:29.033
- I lied.

54:29.099 --> 54:34.071
(ethereal roaring)
(gunfire)

54:41.078 --> 54:44.682
- Look, once you kill
'em, no more virus.

54:44.715 --> 54:47.418
- No, what does that,
what does that mean?

54:47.418 --> 54:49.620
- It means we might
just survive this.

54:49.654 --> 54:52.056
Listen, listen!

54:52.089 --> 54:54.058
It's down to us now.

54:54.058 --> 54:56.026
I know this was your
first day and my last

54:56.026 --> 54:57.995
and I take back
everything I said

54:57.995 --> 54:59.797
about nothing
happening in this town

54:59.797 --> 55:02.800
but this is my town
and I'm not retiring.

55:02.800 --> 55:06.537
I'm gonna make a stand for
it, right here, right now!

55:06.571 --> 55:07.672
Are you with me?

55:07.672 --> 55:08.539
- Fuck yes!

55:10.140 --> 55:11.376
Yeah, come on.

55:11.376 --> 55:12.410
- Well come on!

55:12.443 --> 55:15.245
(shouting)

55:15.245 --> 55:20.250
(eerie tense music)
(ethereal growling)

56:49.006 --> 56:51.241
(shouting)

56:54.111 --> 56:56.380
(shushing)

57:24.709 --> 57:27.545
(low tense music)

58:17.461 --> 58:20.297
(low tense music)

58:54.264 --> 58:56.767
(tense music)

59:15.085 --> 59:17.988
(ethereal roaring)

59:20.557 --> 59:23.527
(guttural snarling)

59:29.133 --> 59:31.636
(tense music)

59:57.461 --> 1:00:01.832
(gunfire)
(roaring)

1:00:34.799 --> 1:00:35.632
- Shaun!

1:00:36.801 --> 1:00:39.970
(gunfire)
(roaring)

1:00:40.004 --> 1:00:40.805
Shaun!

1:00:42.639 --> 1:00:43.741
Shaun.

1:00:43.741 --> 1:00:45.175
- Oh shit.

1:00:45.175 --> 1:00:45.943
Bat!

1:00:48.245 --> 1:00:49.947
They're still coming.

1:00:56.987 --> 1:01:01.826
