1:04:19.789 --> 1:04:21.458
- [Reporter] Hello,
this is Kathy Perkin

1:04:21.458 --> 1:04:24.028
with a channel 13
special news report.

1:04:24.094 --> 1:04:25.462
Breaking live.

1:04:25.462 --> 1:04:27.965
All parts of the
world are under attack

1:04:27.998 --> 1:04:30.968
from what appears to
be alien spaceships.

1:04:30.968 --> 1:04:32.469
I cannot believe I'm saying this

1:04:32.502 --> 1:04:36.540
but reports coming in are
that Toronto, New York,

1:04:36.540 --> 1:04:39.944
Paris, Moscow, and
London have been attacked

1:04:40.010 --> 1:04:42.679
and many famous landmarks
have been destroyed.

1:04:42.712 --> 1:04:45.882
Some world leaders
have been killed.

1:04:45.882 --> 1:04:47.384
We can now see some footage.

1:04:48.618 --> 1:04:51.288
This is like a scene
out of a war movie.

1:04:51.321 --> 1:04:54.992
It's total devastation
and destruction.

1:04:54.992 --> 1:04:56.426
The humanity.

1:04:56.426 --> 1:04:59.596
We don't know how many
causalities there have been

1:04:59.629 --> 1:05:02.532
but early estimates are
it's in the thousands.

1:05:06.136 --> 1:05:07.637
This is not a drill.

1:05:07.671 --> 1:05:10.007
This is a warning from
central government.

1:05:11.575 --> 1:05:13.177
Get away from the cities,

1:05:14.378 --> 1:05:16.880
go to a safe place
in the country.

1:05:18.748 --> 1:05:21.085
Arm yourself if you
can and be ready.

1:05:22.886 --> 1:05:24.054
They are coming.

1:05:25.922 --> 1:05:28.925
(eerie tense music)

1:05:35.299 --> 1:05:37.467
