1:06:33.290 --> 1:06:38.295
(distant screaming)
(flames crackling)

1:06:44.468 --> 1:06:47.471
(eerie tense music)

1:06:51.541 --> 1:06:54.278
- We're gonna need
a bigger boat.

1:06:55.412 --> 1:06:57.247
- So you have seen it then?

1:06:59.183 --> 1:07:00.750
- Of course I have.

1:07:04.388 --> 1:07:05.755
Now let's give em hell.

1:07:09.259 --> 1:07:11.695
- But this time,
